# Type Alias: OnPluginExtension

Plugin extension hook.

## Signature

```ts
export type OnPluginExtension<G> = (ctx: Readonly<CommandContext<G>>, cmd: Readonly<Command<G>>) => Awaitable<void>
```

## Parameters

